de.arm.bot.info

Class ActionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.arm.bot.info.ActionResult

  • public class ActionResult
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing the result the game will send after an action was performed. This is used to interpret the result of the last action and to act accordingly
    Author:
    Team ARM

    • Field Detail

      • ok

        private final boolean ok
        Indicates whether the last action was successful or not. In the protocol the value OK indicates an successful action and the value NOK indicates an unsuccessful action

      • message

        private final java.lang.String message
        The message that was given by the game additionally to the result. The message is used for handling failed action that could occur because of talking etc.
